dc_title_s: Map of Washtenaw County Michigan; drawn and compiled by Frank Krause, C.E.
dc_creator_sm: Krause, Frank.,Everts & Stewart. Combination atlas map of Washtenaw County, Michigan.
dc_description_s: Shows townships, sections, roads, railroads, rivers,, locations of some churches, and some land cover. Advertisements on verso. 1 map: col.; 33 x 39 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
